data.description:
Welcome to 244 Vaughan Street, a serene retreat nestled at the end of a cul-de-sac, ensuring minimal traffic and maximum privacy. This exceptional property offers a host of amenities and features that make it a truly remarkable find in Fort Walton Beach.Generous Space: With 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a sprawling 2,453 square feet of heated/cooled living space (3,225 square feet overall), this home provides plenty of room for comfortable living.RV/Boat Enthusiast's Dream: A side concrete pad is perfect for your RV, boat, or additional parking needs, offering the flexibility you desireMilitary Convenience: Strategically located just minutes from local military bases, this property is an ideal home base for military personnel. Energy Efficiency: This home holds the distinction of being designed with energy efficiency in mind, translating to substantial savings on your utility bills.
Garage with Perks: The oversized 2-car garage features convenient amenities, making maintenance a breeze.
Accessibility: ADA-compliant features ensure comfort for all residents.
Energy-Efficient Insulation: Enjoy a comfortable living environment year-round with insulation throughout.
Quality Builder: Built by an award-winning builder, this home boasts impeccable curb appeal and a solid all-brick exterior.
Value-Added Features: Double-hung windows enhance the value and security of this residence
Gourmet Kitchen: The kitchen is a chef's dream with granite countertops, designer cabinetry, a raised breakfast bar, and a spacious pantry for all your culinary needs.
Schedule a showing today and experience the comfort and convenience it has to offer.
Elegant Dining: The adjacent dining room features an elegant tray ceiling, creating a refined atmosphere for your meals.
Luxurious Master Suite: The large master bedroom boasts a double tray ceiling, adding an extra touch of sophistication. The master bathroom is your private oasis, offering a garden jet tub, a separate shower, a double vanity, and a custom walk-in closet.
Outdoor Delights: Step outside to a sprawling backyard with a concrete pad and a double gate, perfect for your outdoor needs. The covered patio provides an ideal space for relaxation and entertainment, with ample room for future additions, for example: your dream pool!
Quality Construction: This home was meticulously crafted by Watree Homes, ensuring lasting quality and durability.
Don't miss this opportunity to make 244 Vaughan Street your forever home. With its blend of practicality, luxury, and energy efficiency, this property is a rare gem in the real estate market.
